    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a really strong starting point for them. I was thinking of also adding a section about the different ways people interpret this—some people argue it's basically just about fair procedures and the rules the government has to follow. Do you think it's worth mentioning those other views, or would that just confuse the kids when we're trying to show how important it is for civil rights?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
